<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TV87">
<l>pulampuṅ kaṉakuraṟ pōḻvāya vaṉṟilum pūṅkaḻipāyn</l>
<l>talampuṅ kaṉakuraṟ cūḻtirai yāḻiyu māṅkavainiṉ</l>
<l>valampuḷ ḷatunalam pāṭu mitukuṟṟa mākavaiyañ</l>
<l>cilampum paṭiceyva tētiru mālit tiruviṉaiyē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The lamenting, hoarse-voiced Aṉṟil with gaping mouth and the murmuring</l>
<l>hoarse-voiced ocean with surrounding waves, leaping over into the flowered backwaters,</l>
<l>they are like that. She sings the goodness of your strong bird. If this is a fault,</l>
<l>acting in a way that the world resounds [with it], is this the holy work of Tirumāl?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
